      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "deafness and dumbness",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " (Chrysostom, Theophylact, Euthymius Zigabenus, Jansen, Maldonatus, Lightfoot, Grotius, Wolf, and others, including Ewald), against which may be urged ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Luke 1:20",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "; nor is it to be explained by the fact, that we are inclined to communicate by means ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "of signs",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " with dumb people as with deaf people (Bengel, Michaelis, Paulus, Olshausen, de Wette), which can only be arbitrarily applied to Zacharias, since he had only been dumb for a short time and people had previously been accustomed to ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "speak",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " with him. Probably it was only from the wish ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "to spare the mother",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " that the decision of the father, who had all along been listening to the discussion, was called for not aloud, but by signs.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "p",
        "text": "",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "br",
            "class": "",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "br",
            "class": "",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          }
